  "content": "The expert can choose any ten skills to be class skills.\nSkill Points at 1st Level: (6 + Int modifier) x4.\nSkill Points at Each Additional Level: 6 + Int modifier.\nTable: The Expert |\nNPC Level | Base Attack\nBonus | Fort\nSave | Ref\nSave | Will\nSave |\n1st | +0 | +0 | +0 | +2 |\n2nd | +1 | +0 | +0 | +3 |\n3rd | +2 | +1 | +1 | +3 |\n4th | +3 | +1 | +1 | +4 |\n5th | +3 | +1 | +1 | +4 |\n6th | +4 | +2 | +2 | +5 |\n7th | +5 | +2 | +2 | +5 |\n8th | +6/+1 | +2 | +2 | +6 |\n9th | +6/+1 | +3 | +3 | +6 |\n10th | +7/+2 | +3 | +3 | +7 |\n11th | +8/+3 | +3 | +3 | +7 |\n12th | +9/+4 | +4 | +4 | +8 |\n13th | +9/+4 | +4 | +4 | +8 |\n14th | +10/+5 | +4 | +4 | +9 |\n15th | +11/+6/+1 | +5 | +5 | +9 |\n16th | +12/+7/+2 | +5 | +5 | +10 |\n17th | +12/+7/+2 | +5 | +5 | +10 |\n18th | +13/+8/+3 | +6 | +6 | +11 |\n19th | +14/+9/+4 | +6 | +6 | +11 |\n20th | +15/+10/+5 | +6 | +6 | +12 |",
